          "title": "Soliloquy",
          "text": "<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><i><font size=\"3\">Enter Hamlet.</font></i></div><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><font size=\"3\"><i>&nbsp; &nbsp; Ham.</i>&nbsp;To be, or not to be, that is the Que<span style=\"background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); font-family: Junicode, &quot;EB Garamond&quot;, serif; text-align: center; white-space: pre;\">ſ</span>tion:</font></div><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><font size=\"3\">Whether 'tis Nobler in the minde to&nbsp;<span style=\"background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); font-family: Junicode, &quot;EB Garamond&quot;, serif; text-align: center; white-space: pre;\">ſuffer</span></font></div><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); font-family: Junicode, &quot;EB Garamond&quot;, serif; text-align: center; white-space: pre;\"><font size=\"3\">The Slings and Arrowes of outragious Fortune,</font></span></div><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); font-family: Junicode, &quot;EB Garamond&quot;, serif; text-align: center; white-space: pre;\">Or to take Armes again</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); font-family: Junicode, &quot;EB Garamond&quot;, serif; text-align: center; white-space: pre;\">ſt a Sea of troubles,</span></font></div><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); font-family: Junicode, &quot;EB Garamond&quot;, serif; text-align: center; white-space: pre;\">And by oppo</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); font-family: Junicode, &quot;EB Garamond&quot;, serif; text-align: center; white-space: pre;\">ſing end them : to dye, to </span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); font-family: Junicode, &quot;EB Garamond&quot;, serif; text-align: center; white-space: pre;\">ſleepe</span></font></div><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); font-family: Junicode, &quot;EB Garamond&quot;, serif; text-align: center; white-space: pre;\">No more ; and by a </span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); font-family: Junicode, &quot;EB Garamond&quot;, serif; text-align: center; white-space: pre;\">ſleepe, to </span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); font-family: Junicode, &quot;EB Garamond&quot;, serif; text-align: center; white-space: pre;\">ſay we end</span></font></div><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); font-family: Junicode, &quot;EB Garamond&quot;, serif; text-align: center; white-space: pre;\">The Heart-ake, and the thou</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); font-family: Junicode, &quot;EB Garamond&quot;, serif; text-align: center; white-space: pre;\">ſand Naturall </span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); font-family: Junicode, &quot;EB Garamond&quot;, serif; text-align: center; white-space: pre;\">ſhockes</span></font></div>",
